&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;1 inch = 2.54cm&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>延时专题</title><link>/docs/04-by-direction/01.-%E9%9F%B3%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91/%E5%BB%B6%E6%97%B6%E4%B8%93%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 00:27:27 +0800</pubDate><guid>/docs/04-by-direction/01.-%E9%9F%B3%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91/%E5%BB%B6%E6%97%B6%E4%B8%93%E9%A2%98/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;音频在设备端上的延时：&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;音频采集延时&lt;/strong&gt;：采集后的音频首先会经过声卡进行信号转换，声卡本身会产生延时，比如 M-Audio 声卡设备延迟 1ms，

&lt;a class="link link--text" href="https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=6591992&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E8%89%BE%E8%82%AF%E5%A3%B0%E5%8D%A1&amp;zd_token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJ6aGlkYV9zZXJ2ZXIiLCJleHAiOjE3NDcyODgyNTQsInEiOiLoib7ogq_lo7DljaEiLCJ6aGlkYV9zb3VyY2UiOiJlbnRpdHkiLCJjb250ZW50X2lkIjo2NTkxOTkyLCJjb250ZW50X3R5cGUiOiJBcnRpY2xlIiwibWF0Y2hfb3JkZXIiOjEsInpkX3Rva2VuIjpudWxsfQ.fJooL-vw5q4NfrHWEv1pNIee3nvvdi0B_H9iiI-mHI4&amp;zhida_source=entity" rel="external"&gt;艾肯声卡&lt;/a&gt;设备延迟约为 37ms；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;编解码延时&lt;/strong&gt;：随后音频进入前处理、编码的阶段，如果采用 OPUS 

&lt;a class="link link--text" href="https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=6591992&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81&amp;zd_token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJ6aGlkYV9zZXJ2ZXIiLCJleHAiOjE3NDcyODgyNTQsInEiOiLmoIflh4bnvJbnoIEiLCJ6aGlkYV9zb3VyY2UiOiJlbnRpdHkiLCJjb250ZW50X2lkIjo2NTkxOTkyLCJjb250ZW50X3R5cGUiOiJBcnRpY2xlIiwibWF0Y2hfb3JkZXIiOjEsInpkX3Rva2VuIjpudWxsfQ.6OzNeHT6J_ZzCInb0Njias8IcKGf52tKMoNIbhFbFwE&amp;zhida_source=entity" rel="external"&gt;标准编码&lt;/a&gt;，最低算法延时大约需要 2.5~60ms；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;音频播放延时&lt;/strong&gt;：这部分延时与播放端硬件性能相关。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;音频处理延时&lt;/strong&gt;：前后处理，包括 AEC，ANS，AGC 等前后处理算法都会带来算法延时，通常这里的延时就是

&lt;a class="link link--text" href="https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=6591992&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%BB%A4%E6%B3%A2%E5%99%A8%E9%98%B6%E6%95%B0&amp;zd_token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJ6aGlkYV9zZXJ2ZXIiLCJleHAiOjE3NDcyODgyNTQsInEiOiLmu6Tms6LlmajpmLbmlbAiLCJ6aGlkYV9zb3VyY2UiOiJlbnRpdHkiLCJjb250ZW50X2lkIjo2NTkxOTkyLCJjb250ZW50X3R5cGUiOiJBcnRpY2xlIiwibWF0Y2hfb3JkZXIiOjEsInpkX3Rva2VuIjpudWxsfQ.OaEh4LaQE1Q9JbUnJjbIRvvjmRqLnYQx8dipar0QPAk&amp;zhida_source=entity" rel="external"&gt;滤波器阶数&lt;/a&gt;。在 10ms 以内。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;端网络延时&lt;/strong&gt;：这部分延时主要出现在解码之前的 jitter buffer 内，如果在抗丢包处理中，增加了重传算法和前向

&lt;a class="link link--text" href="https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=6591992&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%BA%A0%E9%94%99%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95&amp;zd_token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJ6aGlkYV9zZXJ2ZXIiLCJleHAiOjE3NDcyODgyNTQsInEiOiLnuqDplJnnrpfms5UiLCJ6aGlkYV9zb3VyY2UiOiJlbnRpdHkiLCJjb250ZW50X2lkIjo2NTkxOTkyLCJjb250ZW50X3R5cGUiOiJBcnRpY2xlIiwibWF0Y2hfb3JkZXIiOjEsInpkX3Rva2VuIjpudWxsfQ.QY11hACtHNAVpE3ndRgNYEnZJPY4x-PmIrxiAvKkg7E&amp;zhida_source=entity" rel="external"&gt;纠错算法&lt;/a&gt;，这里的延时一般在 20ms 到 200ms 左右。但是受到 

&lt;a class="link link--text" href="https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=6591992&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=2&amp;q=jitter+buffer&amp;zd_token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJ6aGlkYV9zZXJ2ZXIiLCJleHAiOjE3NDcyODgyNTQsInEiOiJqaXR0ZXIgYnVmZmVyIiwiemhpZGFfc291cmNlIjoiZW50aXR5IiwiY29udGVudF9pZCI6NjU5MTk5MiwiY29udGVudF90eXBlIjoiQXJ0aWNsZSIsIm1hdGNoX29yZGVyIjoyLCJ6ZF90b2tlbiI6bnVsbH0.cBKBNIsKIk_fdstOxxUd156nujRmT9mi80k8JcGMU_g&amp;zhida_source=entity" rel="external"&gt;jitter buffer&lt;/a&gt; 影响，可能会更高。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;视频在设备端上的延时&lt;/strong&gt;：&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>音视频通识</title><link>/docs/04-by-direction/01.-%E9%9F%B3%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91/%E9%9F%B3%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E9%80%9A%E8%AF%86/</link><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 00:27:27 +0800</pubDate><guid>/docs/04-by-direction/01.-%E9%9F%B3%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91/%E9%9F%B3%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E9%80%9A%E8%AF%86/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="h264-h265-常规编码码率snipaste_2026-03-14_23-17-31jpg"&gt;H264 H265 常规编码码率![[Snipaste_2026-03-14_23-17-31.jpg]]&lt;/h2&gt;
